name: Winmonitor
tagline: A Windows monitoring tool that allows you to see who is online across multiple machines given to the program as a text file.  Allows export to CSV for easy sorting.
body:
WinMonitor
==========

A Windows monitoring tool that allows you to see who is online across multiple machines given to the program as a text file.  Allows export to CSV for easy sorting.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
